cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CL 

This paper focuses on deep-network-based hashing for multi-label images, which involves image retrieval and image representation. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper also involves machine learning techniques, which could fall under cs.MM (Multimedia), cs.IR (Information Retrieval), and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Finally, the paper also discusses the use of hash codes for retrieval, which could fall under cs.CL (Computation and Language).
